00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:46,650
[The Peak of True Martial Arts]

25
00:01:46,870 --> 00:01:49,220
[Episode 24]

26
00:01:54,920 --> 00:01:55,600
Have you heard

27
00:01:55,800 --> 00:01:56,480
that the other day,

28
00:01:56,520 --> 00:01:59,320
the Si family invited 20
Bodiless Renewal Realm Warriors

29
00:01:59,360 --> 00:02:01,160
from the Kou family in Qingxuan City
to the Nie family,

30
00:02:01,160 --> 00:02:02,760
but none of them came out?

31
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:05,600
You mean the transcendental family
in Qingxuan City?

32
00:02:05,720 --> 00:02:06,600
No way.

33
00:02:06,800 --> 00:02:08,760
There is a world of difference
in the ability of the two families.

34
00:02:08,840 --> 00:02:10,840
The warriors of the Kou family didn't come out.

35
00:02:11,160 --> 00:02:13,600
Besides, even the Si family has been
removed from a list in Qinghe Bay.

36
00:02:13,720 --> 00:02:17,200
I heard that there was a Transcendental Strong Warrior
in the Kou family in Qingxuan City.

37
00:02:17,400 --> 00:02:19,000
Alas, if that's the case,

38
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:20,960
he will seek vengeance.

39
00:02:20,960 --> 00:02:22,120
Yeah, he will surely do that.

40
00:02:22,480 --> 00:02:24,840
I just wonder if the Nie family can survive.

41
00:02:25,760 --> 00:02:27,440
Everyone understands that,

42
00:02:27,520 --> 00:02:29,360
so now all forces in Qinghe Bay

43
00:02:29,480 --> 00:02:31,080
don't dare to be very close to the Nie family,

44
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:33,160
fearing that they will be
implicated in the future.

45
00:02:33,600 --> 00:02:36,320
(With Nie Feng around, they're worried for nothing.)

46
00:02:54,880 --> 00:02:56,920
The Kou family should know the news.

47
00:02:57,200 --> 00:02:58,880
Before that Transcendental Strong Warrior comes,

48
00:02:59,320 --> 00:03:00,920
I must hurry to speed up

49
00:03:01,480 --> 00:03:02,800
the improvement of Cultivation.

50
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:05,600
(From Qingxuan City to Qinghe Bay,)

51
00:03:06,120 --> 00:03:08,520
(it will only take one day to arrive downstream.)

52
00:03:09,280 --> 00:03:11,800
(And it will only take one and a half days
to go back to Qingxuan City)

53
00:03:12,240 --> 00:03:13,840
(from Qinghe Bay upstream.)

54
00:03:14,480 --> 00:03:16,680
(Even if they stayed for half a day
at the Si family after that,)

55
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:18,760
(they should have come back
within three days at most.)

56
00:03:19,880 --> 00:03:21,200
(Besides, if they got held up,)

57
00:03:21,640 --> 00:03:23,160
(they should have had the message sent to me.)

58
00:03:23,480 --> 00:03:24,600
(It's been over 5 days.)

59
00:03:24,960 --> 00:03:26,440
(Why haven't the people I sent come back yet?)

60
00:03:27,080 --> 00:03:28,160
Elder Hao Yang,

61
00:03:28,280 --> 00:03:30,160
bad news.

62
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:32,200
The warriors who went to Qinghe Bay...

63
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:32,920
What's wrong with them?

64
00:03:33,600 --> 00:03:35,560
They are all dead.

65
00:03:35,920 --> 00:03:36,480
What?

66
00:03:37,520 --> 00:03:38,720
All dead?

67
00:03:39,480 --> 00:03:41,680
They are a good
20 Bodiless Renewal Realm Warriors

68
00:03:42,520 --> 00:03:44,200
who are all the elite people
of Bodiless Renewal Realm of the Kou family.

69
00:03:46,120 --> 00:03:47,200
Didn't Si Yang Fu say

70
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:49,320
there were only two Bodiless Renewal Realm
Warriors in the Nie family?

71
00:03:49,600 --> 00:03:51,960
I sent 20 Bodiless Renewal Realm Warriors.

72
00:03:52,120 --> 00:03:53,520
How could they be all dead?

73
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:55,720
I heard that on that day, Si Yang Fu

74
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:58,360
went to Nie's Residence with another
Bodiless Renewal Realm Warrior of the Si family,

75
00:03:58,520 --> 00:04:00,040
Si Xing Yun, 100 elite people of the Si family,

76
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:02,600
and our 20

77
00:04:02,720 --> 00:04:04,360
Bodiless Renewal Realm Warriors.

78
00:04:04,560 --> 00:04:07,200
In the end, only nine people of the Si family
escaped from Nie's Residence,

79
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:09,320
but later they were chased and killed.

80
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:11,720
The others didn't come out alive.

81
00:04:12,160 --> 00:04:14,520
Now the Si family has been eradicated
in Qinghe Bay.

82
00:04:14,600 --> 00:04:16,360
No one knows what exactly happened

83
00:04:16,360 --> 00:04:17,760
at Nie's Residence on that day.

84
00:04:19,959 --> 00:04:21,399
Oh, right. I also heard

85
00:04:21,560 --> 00:04:24,000
that the nine people

86
00:04:24,200 --> 00:04:27,280
were all killed by the son
of the head of the Nie family, Nie Feng.

87
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:29,320
According to those witnesses,

88
00:04:29,480 --> 00:04:31,760
I feel the moves Nie Feng used

89
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:33,320
are a bit like Transcendental Martial Arts.

90
00:04:33,400 --> 00:04:35,000
Is he the Nie Feng that Kou Hong Yu and Kou Yu

91
00:04:35,000 --> 00:04:36,680
waited at the Nie family?

92
00:04:37,280 --> 00:04:38,160
Yeah.

93
00:04:38,280 --> 00:04:39,800
He's quite weird.

94
00:04:39,840 --> 00:04:41,880
I heard that he has suffered from Toxic Heat
since he was a kid,

95
00:04:42,040 --> 00:04:43,160
so he can't cultivate his skills at all.

96
00:04:43,400 --> 00:04:46,600
However, a few months ago, his Toxic Heat
suddenly disappeared.

97
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:48,920
(Besides, his cultivation speed improves
by leaps and bounds.)

98
00:04:50,400 --> 00:04:52,160
(He once defeated Kou Yu's guard
who was in Blood Changing Realm)

99
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:54,520
(with the cultivation of Chakras Opening Realm.)

100
00:04:54,680 --> 00:04:57,720
(Now he has even reached the later stage
of Bodiless Renewal Realm.)

101
00:04:57,880 --> 00:04:59,200
(It's very unusual.)

102
00:04:59,400 --> 00:05:01,360
I think Nie Feng must be the key figure.

103
00:05:01,440 --> 00:05:04,640
Our warriors were very likely to die at his hands.

104
00:05:05,040 --> 00:05:06,560
A man in the later stage
of Bodiless Renewal Realm

105
00:05:06,800 --> 00:05:09,480
can defeat our 20
Bodiless Renewal Realm Warriors?

106
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:11,000
From what I've seen,

107
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:12,600
his ability

108
00:05:12,640 --> 00:05:14,600
is far higher than his own cultivation.

109
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:17,840
You see, he can defeat Blood Changing Realm
just with Chakras Opening Realm.

110
00:05:18,120 --> 00:05:20,680
Now he has reached the later stage
of Bodiless Renewal Realm.

111
00:05:20,920 --> 00:05:22,360
His real ability

112
00:05:22,440 --> 00:05:25,160
might have reached the realm
of True Martial Arts.

113
00:05:25,440 --> 00:05:27,200
What matters more is his cultivation speed.

114
00:05:27,480 --> 00:05:30,280
Even the intelligent disciples
of the major sects

115
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:31,520
in the world

116
00:05:31,640 --> 00:05:34,440
can't become the Bodiless Renewal Realm Warriors
within just a few months.

117
00:05:34,720 --> 00:05:37,160
I guess he must have
experienced something unusual.

118
00:05:39,560 --> 00:05:41,040
I have to go to Qinghe Sect again

119
00:05:41,160 --> 00:05:42,680
and invite Patriarch back as soon as possible.

120
00:05:43,080 --> 00:05:44,480
Our family has such a disaster,

121
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:46,320
so the Nie family must pay the price.

122
00:05:52,400 --> 00:05:54,760
[Kou's Residence]
(There are nine domains in Nine Domains Mainland.)

123
00:05:54,880 --> 00:05:57,720
(Besides Yanhuang Domain
connecting eight domains,)

124
00:05:57,880 --> 00:06:00,600
(the other eight domains are occupied
by the major eight sects.)

125
00:06:00,760 --> 00:06:04,160
(They hold the principle that one sect
controls one domain.)

126
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:05,320
(Among them,)

127
00:06:05,360 --> 00:06:07,680
(Pontiff Hao Tian's territory, Haotian Domain,)

128
00:06:07,680 --> 00:06:09,000
(is divided into 13 prefectures.)

129
00:06:09,080 --> 00:06:12,440
[Qingsu City]
(Places such as Qinghe Bay, Qingxuan City, and Qingsu City)

130
00:06:12,600 --> 00:06:15,760
(are all part of Qingzhou Prefecture,
in the east of Haotian Domain.)

131
00:06:15,800 --> 00:06:18,720
(Qinghe Sect is a large sect
in Qingzhou Prefecture.)

132
00:06:18,760 --> 00:06:20,960
[Prince Kou Ding's Residence]
(The sect has close ties with Pontiff Hao Tian.)

133
00:06:21,240 --> 00:06:22,440
(Its territories include)

134
00:06:22,440 --> 00:06:24,920
(many cities that center on Qingsu City.)

135
00:06:34,880 --> 00:06:36,280
Greetings, sir.

136
00:06:36,760 --> 00:06:38,600
Thanks for your hard work.

137
00:06:45,040 --> 00:06:46,320
What's wrong with him?

138
00:06:49,520 --> 00:06:50,360
Here's the thing.

139
00:06:50,520 --> 00:06:53,360
This time, he went all the way
to Qinghe City to buy things.

140
00:06:53,840 --> 00:06:56,360
But the quality goods had been bought
by the Star Ocean Chamber of Commerce.

141
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:58,560
He only bought some inferior goods.

142
00:06:58,720 --> 00:07:00,280
So he's in a very bad mood.

143
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:02,480
Mr. Kou.

144
00:07:02,680 --> 00:07:03,360
What is it?

145
00:07:03,880 --> 00:07:05,480
Someone from the Kou family wants to see you.

146
00:07:05,880 --> 00:07:07,880
He's waited for you at your residence for 10 days.

147
00:07:08,320 --> 00:07:09,040
Got it.

148
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:15,040
Although you're relaxed,

149
00:07:15,720 --> 00:07:17,480
you will be furious

150
00:07:17,600 --> 00:07:19,080
after hearing the news of the Kou family.

151
00:07:19,360 --> 00:07:20,120
What did you say?

152
00:07:30,640 --> 00:07:32,600
Please calm down.

153
00:07:33,200 --> 00:07:35,360
How dare an ordinary martial arts family

154
00:07:35,400 --> 00:07:37,440
do such a thing to my family!

155
00:07:37,520 --> 00:07:39,960
I will wipe out the Nie family of Qinghe Bay.

156
00:07:40,960 --> 00:07:42,880
I wonder when you intend to set out.

157
00:07:43,480 --> 00:07:45,720
Of course now.

158
00:08:05,120 --> 00:08:07,880
The one who can fly in the sky
is a Transcendental Strong Warrior.

159
00:08:11,680 --> 00:08:14,720
Is he the Transcendental Patriarch
of the Kou family,

160
00:08:14,760 --> 00:08:15,800
Kou Ding Hou?

161
00:08:15,840 --> 00:08:18,000
My goodness, even the Transcendental
Strong Warrior is here.

162
00:08:18,040 --> 00:08:19,760
Something bad will happen to the Nie family.

163
00:08:20,480 --> 00:08:21,680
Where's Nie's Residence?

164
00:08:28,320 --> 00:08:29,520
Within this half a month,

165
00:08:29,680 --> 00:08:31,600
I take in Yuanling Stone every day
to improve my skills.

166
00:08:31,960 --> 00:08:33,720
I've reached the peak of Bodiless Renewal Realm

167
00:08:34,039 --> 00:08:35,479
and I can become bodiless.

168
00:08:35,880 --> 00:08:37,120
As long as I finish changing bones,

169
00:08:37,120 --> 00:08:39,240
I can enter True Martial Arts
from Ordinary martial arts

170
00:08:39,480 --> 00:08:40,720
and become a Transcendental Strong Warrior.

